title: Forth Grade Nothing - over half of unreleased album and full 7
description:
Forth Grade Nothing, punk band who are no longer together and haven&#039;t been for a very long time. They had made a s/t album but due to label issues it was never released. You may of heard a few of their tracks on the film "Bi0-Dome", they did the song "Adirectional" on the opening credits and the cover of "kid&#039;s in america" also in the film.

This is just over half of their album (missing about 7 tracks, impossible to find) the quality of most isn&#039;t great, but it isn&#039;t bad either, demo quality if you will.

Also Includes their 7" EP "Jack Frost" which was the only thing actually released by them.
